items.sentence: Do you care what other people think about you?
Do you know any Canadians living in Australia?
Do you know how many people live in Australia?
I know for certain that that\'s what happened.
I know quite a few people who don\'t eat meat.
I know that Tom can\'t speak French very well.
I know that you don\'t speak French very well.
Tom shouldn\'t always believe what others say.
Tom shouldn\'t have given Mary a diamond ring.
Tom shouldn\'t have gone to Boston by himself.
